{"tid":882754,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"IBM 宣佈成功以 2667 億港元收購 Red Hat","createTime":"2018-10-30T10:46:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T14:49:36.000Z","uid":1886,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"12c6038d021f37a5064537758e4611d1b7353596","tid":882754,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T10:46:11.000Z","msg":"IBM 在美國時間 10 月 28 日宣佈已完成收購 Linux 陣營中最大套件開發商 Red Hat，收購價為 340 億美元（約2667億港元），以強化雲端業務，雙方預期將會在 2019 年下半年完成交易。這單交易是 IBM 公司史上最大規模的收購行動。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/l_yu_ibm1-1200x660.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2Fl_yu_ibm1-1200x660.jpg&h=b22d348b&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\nIBM 表示將會以每股 190 美元的現金價收購 Red Hat 股票，總值為 340 億美元。收購價與 Red Hat 在上周五的收市價 116.68 美元相比溢價達到 63%。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/l_yu_ibm2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2Fl_yu_ibm2.jpg&h=f36072ee&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\nIBM 成功收購 Red Hat 之後，將編入到 IBM 的混合雲端（Hybrid cloud）服務隊伍中，以一個獨立部門的方式繼續運作。Red Hat 公司 CEO Jim Whitehurst 會加入資深管理團隊，將直接隸屬於 IBM 公司 CEO，Ginni Rometty 之下。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/10/29/linuxredhatibm/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F10%2F29%2Flinuxredhatibm%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=em5p5Bj%2FDsQIOLZmEY4XRv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=ae2475c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/10/29/linuxredhatibm/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"eda2ad6645e140d6b605f791c8593d3eb7b4fa85","tid":882754,"uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T10:46:49.000Z","msg":"IBM 表示在收購完成後，可讓他們成為世界領先的「複合雲供應商」，同時提供本地雲與外部雲服務。而 Rad Hat 開源的特性將會是公司發展的主軸。兩間公司表示即使在合併後，仍然會保持開源的政策，並繼續對社群作出貢獻，而 Red Hat 產品仍然會在市面上流通。<br />\n<br />\n根據 CNBC 報道，IBM 今次收購是該公司最大的收購案，而且也是美國科技業界第 3 大併購案。"},{"pid":"93fe2e1978a658618b67c681e503653ae41b7992","tid":882754,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T11:01:35.000Z","msg":"收購價與 Red Hat 在上周五的收市價 116.68 美元相比溢價達到 63%<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f828440af66e3a773674d57fa8c757cb6cb7bf2d","tid":882754,"uid":41887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T11:29:56.000Z","msg":"opensource is conquering the world <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c627292b0e0f1b24acedb3426a351d9ae9e0214","tid":882754,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T01:23:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"></span>"},{"pid":"24b97be323ca9e1c00b12cbeb400f7b10f8e202e","tid":882754,"uid":28563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T01:57:20.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"518c4c422bb41512cd25112838171b6172dedea9","tid":882754,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T02:56:12.000Z","msg":"redhat d enterprise packages 咁值錢㗎咩？"},{"pid":"2023ef52188210e86d2fa45cb19d7d5169717fdb","tid":882754,"uid":10009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T06:04:15.000Z","msg":"咁咪等open source user 比錢買返佢囉<br />\nOh <br />\nUser: it is free, isn&rsquo;t it?"},{"pid":"35de92925025d4edd82d692373fb5da53777d8a9","tid":882754,"uid":60249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T14:49:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}